Package org.robots.ni

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Positions  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    This class contains all the constants of the project.
    Coordinates
    This class is the starting point after reading the input from the file.It calls the main controller of the robot from which it gets the bounds and initial positions of the robot and finally it will give the destination position of the robot
    Heading
    This class do the actual operations of robot by taking the directions and depending upon the input it will move the robot
    Plateau
    This class reads instructions from a file and process the instructions.
    PlateauTest
    This class check for the input file in the current directory
    PositionsImpl
    This class read the operations from the file and set the initial position,bounds and also set the data to which place robot need to move and it also validates the input instructions from the file.
    ResourceFile  
    Robot
    This class contains all the operations require to move the robot from current position.
    RobotController
    This class is the controller of the robot which moves the robot position depending upon the input file
